---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
const updated = "2026-05-26";
---
<BaseLayout title="Terms of Use" description="ZoroTreeking terms of use">
  <article class="max-w-prose mx-auto px-5 pt-16 pb-24">
    <h1 class="font-serif text-5xl sm:text-6xl leading-[0.95] tracking-tight mb-6">Terms of Use</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-[var(--text-tertiary)] mb-8">Last updated: {updated}</p>

    <div class="prose prose-neutral dark:prose-invert max-w-none">

      <h2>1. About this site</h2>
      <p>ZoroTreeking is the personal blog of Zoro, covering AI learning, investment, photography and hiking. It is a <strong>non-commercial personal site</strong> — no commerce, no transactions, no public account registration, and no third-party uploads or forwarding.</p>

      <h2>2. What we offer</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Static articles authored or curated by the owner</li>
        <li>Pageview analytics and per-article like/dislike feedback</li>
        <li>An AI chat widget for study purposes, with input filtered by a keyword list</li>
        <li>RSS feed and full-text search</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>3. User conduct</h2>
      <p>Visitors must comply with the laws of the People's Republic of China. You must <strong>not</strong>:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Submit content via the AI chat that violates Chinese law, harms others, or promotes violence / pornography / drugs / terrorism</li>
        <li>Bypass the keyword filter, rate limit, or other technical protections</li>
        <li>Scan, scrape, DDoS, brute-force, or otherwise attack the site</li>
        <li>Abuse the feedback feature with bots or coordinated voting</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Violations will be blocked, logged, and where required, reported to authorities.</p>

      <h2>4. Disclaimers</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Articles reflect personal opinions and notes — <strong>not investment, medical or legal advice</strong>.</li>
        <li>AI assistant responses are generated by language models and may be <strong>inaccurate, outdated or wrong</strong>. Always verify.</li>
        <li>Third-party references (papers, news, images) remain under their original copyright; cited only for study and discussion.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>5. Intellectual property</h2>
      <p>Original content (articles, code, design, photos) is owned by Zoro. The site code is MIT-licensed on <a href="https://github.com/lzf00/zorotreeking">GitHub</a>. To repost articles, contact <a href="mailto:1437066318@qq.com">1437066318@qq.com</a> and keep the source link.</p>

      <h2>6. Availability</h2>
      <p>We strive for stability but make no uptime guarantee. Maintenance and force majeure may cause downtime.</p>

      <h2>7. Changes</h2>
      <p>These terms may be updated as regulations or services evolve. Updates take effect upon publication. Material changes will be announced on the homepage for 7 days.</p>

      <h2>8. Governing law</h2>
      <p>These terms are governed by the laws of the People's Republic of China. Disputes are first attempted via negotiation; otherwise jurisdiction lies with courts in Shanghai.</p>

      <h2>9. Contact</h2>
      <p><a href="mailto:1437066318@qq.com">1437066318@qq.com</a> · Operator: Zoro · <a href="https://beian.miit.gov.cn/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">沪 ICP 备 2026021578 号-1</a></p>

      <hr />
      <p class="text-sm text-[var(--text-tertiary)]">Related: <a href="/en/privacy">Privacy</a> · <a href="/en/contact">Contact / Abuse</a></p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
